# Track pre-seeded corpus (src/agentalloy/_corpus/agentalloy.duck + fragments.lance/)
# so a fresh clone is a working install. The corpus ships inside the wheel as
# package data; on first run it's copied to the user data dir. Ignore
# runtime telemetry, per-install scratch, and any tmp build artifacts.
src/agentalloy/_corpus/**/*-shm
src/agentalloy/_corpus/**/*-wal
data/
!src/agentalloy/_corpus/
*.db
*.sqlite
*.sqlite3

